      FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
      "f3c902fe-fb8c-4d05-9d36-449613146b4c"],
     " is supposed to be the matrix representation of a multi-qubit system \
and hence a ",
     Cell[BoxData[
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox["2", 
        StyleBox["n", "TI"]], "\[Times]", 
       SuperscriptBox["2", 
        StyleBox["n", "TI"]]}]], "InlineFormula",
      FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
      "68392c14-15b6-4631-96c4-eb2f166ac3e7"],
